history.content: Please email me directly to receive the CPT form and learn the steps you will need to take before I can issue the CCN.

I'm an international student EECS major and got a summer internship offer a while ago. However, I forgot to apply for CPT and my job will start next Wednesday. I know I need to register CS97 for summer and also get a recommendation signature from my department. So may I ask, what is the CCN for CS97 for summer? And also who should I get this signature from? Unfortunately CPT takes 3 days to issue so I don't know if I can make it. Thanks!
history.subject: Summer internship telebear register and signature
